Package: symbiosis-email
Architecture: all
Depends: exim4-daemon-heavy, spamassassin, dovecot-imapd, dovecot-pop3d, clamav-daemon, ruby, perl, libsys-syslog-perl, adduser, make, rdoc, ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: symbiosis-common
Replaces: bytemark-vhost-email
Recommends: symbiosis-webmail-roundcube | symbiosis-webmail-squirrelmail
Conflicts: bytemark-vhost-email, symbiosis-monit (<< 2011:1206)
Description: A complete virtual hosting solution for email
 This package contains the infrastructure and configuration for a
 virtual hosting setup with full support for:
 .
  * Virtual Hosting
  * Address Rewriting
  * IMAP + IMAPS
  * POP3 + POP3S
  * SMTP
  * Sieve

Package: symbiosis-webmail-squirrelmail
Architecture: all
Depends: squirrelmail
Conflicts: symbiosis-webmail-roundcube
Description: SquirrelMail configured as the default webmail client for Symbiosis
 Installs SquirrelMail and its dependencies as the default mail client for
 machines running Symbiosis.

Package: symbiosis-webmail-roundcube
Architecture: all
Depends: roundcube (>> 0.5), roundcube-mysql, roundcube-plugins
Conflicts: symbiosis-webmail-squirrelmail
Description: Roundcube configured as the default webmail client for Symbiosis
 Installs Roundcube and its dependencies as the default webmail client for
 Symbiosis.  Roundcube is a modern client that is configured to include support
 for Sieve filters.

